Cell[CellGroupData[{
Cell["\<\
xAct test notebook: single-notebook workflow with abstract perturbations\
\>", "Title",ExpressionUUID->"8638e129-965f-fe4d-90e1-17c5801f5440"],

Cell["\<\
This notebook is a minimal working template for the workflow we discussed: \
first build the theory abstractly with xTras+xPert, then keep the result \
available for later specialization to concrete backgrounds in the same kernel.

Example theory: a free massive scalar field on a general curved background. \
This is used only as a simple test case.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"1aed1a61-e0be-724a-b565-23eef6b62d64"],

